Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.13,0:01:49.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就再進行一次作戰確認
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.21,0:01:53.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和蒼的熊隊乘坐師堂的汽車
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.59,0:01:56.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去往阻止往『七鄉』送入妖力的發生源
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.05,0:01:57.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.77,0:02:02.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼長頸鹿組秋名和恭助拖住在城鎮暴走的妖怪
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.42,0:02:04.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把危害降到最低限
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.54,0:02:06.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以上 有什麼問題嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.65,0:02:07.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有一個問題
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.53,0:02:08.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼請說 恭助
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.28,0:02:10.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隊名的意義是？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.46,0:02:11.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有 其他呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.34,0:02:13.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無所謂的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.55,0:02:15.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至少用A隊B隊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.86,0:02:16.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,駁回
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.92,0:02:19.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真抱歉 是小車
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.92,0:02:21.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 足夠了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.20,0:02:25.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起 讓你做這種危險的工作
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.26,0:02:26.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係的 反正破爛車
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.22,0:02:28.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小心一點去
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.83,0:02:31.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那邊也只有2人不要逞強哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.79,0:02:33.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.14,0:02:34.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不需要擔心的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.20,0:02:37.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,立刻就會發現的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.44,0:02:38.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們等著
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.55,0:02:39.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.88,0:02:46.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要逞強…嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.99,0:02:52.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在不逞強 什麼時候做呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.44,0:02:52.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吶
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.54,0:02:54.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同感
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.18,0:02:57.86,TITLE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(800,1000)}{\pos(318,325)}你的面前
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.69,0:03:11.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放哪去了 可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.67,0:03:29.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.64,0:03:32.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該有播送去元老院避難的要求
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.00,0:03:35.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼 有忘記的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.34,0:03:39.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,町長沒事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.50,0:03:42.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在醫院的床上休息著
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.48,0:03:44.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,醫院？發生了什麼嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.89,0:03:46.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是稍做休息而已
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.74,0:03:50.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相對的我來代替小姐來戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.33,0:03:52.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.81,0:03:54.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說過我來戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.60,0:04:01.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和妹妹桃華不論在哪裡都受到人類的欺負
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.40,0:04:06.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為討厭那種生活 逃到山中生活時
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.49,0:04:08.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小姐來了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.00,0:04:15.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人只有被保護過才會明白去保護別人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.27,0:04:17.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來櫻真町吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.90,0:04:25.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被小姐保護著我來到這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.26,0:04:32.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了小姐我來戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.25,0:04:34.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快離開這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.84,0:04:35.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.73,0:04:49.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下面怎麼走 吶…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.41,0:04:52.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蒼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.86,0:04:55.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,左…不應該是右吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.42,0:05:00.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪邊呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.22,0:05:01.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不明白
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.91,0:05:05.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,漂浮在空氣中的妖氣\N不是這樣簡單就可以捕捉到的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.95,0:05:07.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.27,0:05:09.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 因為沒有形態
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.54,0:05:12.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要著急 慢慢來 要確定好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.40,0:05:14.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.57,0:05:15.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.14,0:05:16.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是樹裡小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.30,0:05:19.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 喂 我們這邊還沒什麼進展
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.89,0:05:25.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂 蒼？現在姬剛睡…喂?喂?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.66,0:05:31.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 喂 圈外？到底在哪哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.69,0:05:39.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姬 成為町長已經多少年了？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.47,0:05:41.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,6年
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.58,0:05:46.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對吧 稍微讓大家等一等 大家都不會計較的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.07,0:05:47.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.09,0:05:51.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說了交給秋名 妳不也同意了的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.42,0:06:01.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.29,0:06:05.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是果然還是不能輸啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.16,0:06:07.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等 住手
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.78,0:06:08.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.81,0:06:14.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是個不服輸的孩子呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.58,0:06:18.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,疼疼疼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.29,0:06:20.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,意外的硬腦袋呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.16,0:06:33.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,『調率』
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.91,0:06:48.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,影子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.24,0:06:50.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,秋名
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.11,0:06:52.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別過來 妖怪要是碰到會受傷的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.43,0:06:54.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,『調率』
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.96,0:07:02.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,『調率』不要用過頭
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.00,0:07:04.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要緊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.04,0:07:06.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是稍微有點運動不足而已
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.38,0:07:09.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在關鍵時候派不上用處會很困擾的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.21,0:07:11.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在還沒問題不是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.05,0:07:12.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在而已
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.78,0:07:13.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.47,0:07:14.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.16,0:07:16.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.75,0:07:19.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使面對円神也可以『調率』的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.71,0:07:21.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身體沒問題
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.10,0:07:22.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是問這個問題
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.34,0:07:23.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在想
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.37,0:07:25.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要聽結論
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.19,0:07:28.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出現在眼前時會做出結論的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.88,0:07:32.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…做不到的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.80,0:07:48.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.41,0:07:53.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說蜥蜴怎麼減少了 是你們所為嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.06,0:07:55.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,寵物的話題禁止
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.53,0:07:59.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎 那還真不清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.95,0:08:00.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恭助
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.36,0:08:01.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.70,0:08:08.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恭助
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.81,0:08:12.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果是動作快的傢伙就先說出來
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.63,0:08:14.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說之前就跳出去了不是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.28,0:08:19.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使明白我的特性 也無能為力
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.23,0:08:22.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不像那傢伙是那樣的笨蛋呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.17,0:08:26.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎 我以為是一樣的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.69,0:08:37.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,100%的純正妖怪\N 竟然還不明白円神大人的理想 蠢貨
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.35,0:08:41.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我收回去 把我和那笨蛋相比的話收回去
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.02,0:08:42.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.36,0:08:44.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無聊的妖怪
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.47,0:08:55.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了城鎮 為了小姐而戰鬥這就是我的信念
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.44,0:09:08.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,右邊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.32,0:09:11.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,師堂 影子呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.19,0:09:13.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,漸漸增加著
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.28,0:09:16.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,樹枝也比之前生長了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.49,0:09:19.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蒼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.63,0:09:20.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,左邊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.96,0:09:29.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 可以走的路越來越少了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.66,0:09:35.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.37,0:09:49.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,八重小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.03,0:09:52.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到妖力源的地址了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.45,0:09:55.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妖力很難捕捉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.96,0:09:58.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那雙可愛的耳朵是為了什麼而長的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.39,0:10:01.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是是沒有形狀的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.93,0:10:03.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想知道的是發生源不是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.06,0:10:05.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,方法只是這樣？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.55,0:10:08.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.35,0:10:13.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用汽車載著跑 不是會變得難以捕捉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.98,0:10:20.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,電波會通過什麼地方呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.30,0:10:23.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.42,0:10:28.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,八重那傢伙又要遭罰款了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.38,0:10:29.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.85,0:10:30.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,閉嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.10,0:10:33.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.79,0:10:41.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這種地方一動不動 點都不舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.13,0:10:42.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.03,0:10:44.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可以的 水奈
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.55,0:10:47.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在秋名他們回來之前要待在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.26,0:10:50.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好怕
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.55,0:10:51.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,待在這裡就沒問題
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.06,0:10:53.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再忍耐一會
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.85,0:10:55.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是在開玩笑的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.16,0:11:01.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在我們的靈鏈因為円神的妖力而失去了效果
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.05,0:11:03.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我們要砍掉它嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.70,0:11:08.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對 現在只保護城鎮中的妖怪就已經是極限
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.83,0:11:10.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有砍掉『七鄉』…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.12,0:11:10.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我拒絕
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.93,0:11:12.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你沒有拒絕的權利
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.03,0:11:14.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在立刻去
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.17,0:11:18.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行 現在還有想要保護城鎮的人在
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.73,0:11:21.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是說町長和事務所的人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.55,0:11:26.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些傢伙最喜歡這個人和妖共存的城鎮
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.89,0:11:29.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對保護這裡而感覺到榮耀
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.50,0:11:33.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是絕對不想讓城鎮消失而已
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.22,0:11:36.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這哪裡不對了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.93,0:11:41.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還只是力量沒有完全使用出來而已
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.26,0:11:45.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還想再等一等
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.16,0:11:47.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再等一會
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.15,0:12:03.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.41,0:12:12.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,『廣域讀心』
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.43,0:12:17.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蒼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.30,0:12:18.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.98,0:12:20.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看到了…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.73,0:12:22.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人們的思念…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.76,0:12:26.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是『覺』的…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.16,0:12:33.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.27,0:12:35.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.64,0:12:45.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,東京鐵塔
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.90,0:13:16.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.39,0:13:22.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是被命令要休息嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.63,0:13:26.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以才說妳不行的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.22,0:13:29.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說的對
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.54,0:13:32.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓街道變成這種情況
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.63,0:13:34.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給大家添了麻煩
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.81,0:13:36.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說什麼被人和龍所愛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.41,0:13:38.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和婆婆完全不一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.41,0:13:40.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.86,0:13:43.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前代和妳不一樣是個膽小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.58,0:13:47.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼都做不來 總是被別人所救
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.74,0:13:49.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.59,0:13:50.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事實而已
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.71,0:13:52.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,婆婆嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.51,0:13:59.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是被愛著 被人 城鎮和龍所愛著
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.98,0:14:01.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被愛著…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.25,0:14:07.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帶著這個出去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.82,0:14:16.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個是？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.09,0:14:18.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓她去沒關係吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.88,0:14:22.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 已經沒關係了 真是健壯的身體呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.35,0:14:25.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和石頭腦袋一樣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.68,0:14:26.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說的對
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.86,0:14:32.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是前代使用的「龍槍」之刃
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.46,0:14:35.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是否充分練習過了 讓我看看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.92,0:14:37.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.78,0:14:45.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那邊也缺少人手
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.60,0:14:47.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,九街區的人已經朝那邊去了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.23,0:14:48.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.58,0:14:49.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,町長
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.54,0:14:53.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼可以來這種地方 這種事由我們來做
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.64,0:14:56.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,城鎮有可能會消失不是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.32,0:14:59.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們也想保護好自己的城鎮啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.45,0:15:01.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,保護？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.51,0:15:05.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 去二街區了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.50,0:15:06.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.85,0:15:09.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.98,0:15:11.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.18,0:15:16.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那邊的道路有電線桿倒了 很危險
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.17,0:15:19.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然遠點 但從這邊繞過去比較好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.45,0:15:21.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.52,0:15:23.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.63,0:15:25.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.59,0:15:26.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.86,0:15:32.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加油 町長
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.26,0:15:38.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我曾經想過不可以依靠著什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.96,0:15:42.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,城鎮的力量 人們的力量 龍的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.94,0:15:46.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必須全部由自己的力量來做什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.51,0:15:51.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不然的話 便不會被愛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.82,0:15:53.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會被任何人所愛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.09,0:16:00.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 並不是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.12,0:16:04.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,並不是力量 並不是義務
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.35,0:16:06.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而是信任
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.43,0:16:16.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朝鐵路去就可以了吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.38,0:16:19.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 盡量選擇有最長直線的路徑
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.96,0:16:20.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瞭解
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.40,0:16:26.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果言靈使吃下了潤喉糖會怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.25,0:16:28.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓你們瞭解瞭解
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.50,0:16:41.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,『鬼』的力量竟然如此強大
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.46,0:16:47.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明有這樣的力量 為什麼還會與円神對立
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.66,0:16:50.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正因為有力量 才要保護小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.43,0:16:55.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她是讓你即使捨身也要保護的人物嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.60,0:16:59.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是在挑釁 給他點顏色看看
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.86,0:17:00.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我收回
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.45,0:17:24.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看 那個『七鄉』
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.21,0:17:30.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再過一會 美妙的世界就會降臨
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.99,0:17:35.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有妨礙我們的傢伙 沒有人類的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.42,0:17:37.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,囉嗦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.56,0:17:38.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恭助
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.65,0:17:39.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別過來
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.49,0:17:47.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,『調率』
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.25,0:17:55.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,秋名 哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.03,0:18:09.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,『調率』…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.65,0:18:12.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,桃華 為什麼妳會在這種地方
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.04,0:18:14.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為很擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.33,0:18:15.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回到元老院去
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.10,0:18:15.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.83,0:18:16.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,桃華
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.37,0:18:17.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冷靜點
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.59,0:18:18.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂 住手
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.96,0:18:20.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在只需考慮円神的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.40,0:18:23.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妖力發生源找到了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.36,0:18:24.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蒼找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.97,0:18:25.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地點是？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.36,0:18:27.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,東京鐵塔
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.19,0:18:32.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,長度30米 鐵製物
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.64,0:18:36.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中央為長度21米強勁的鐵質管狀物
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.22,0:18:38.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下部有移動用車輪
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.89,0:18:41.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前方12個 後方12個
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.08,0:18:42.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,言葉？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.04,0:18:43.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說交給她
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.12,0:18:45.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用平時的88MM砲？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.70,0:18:47.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個貌似打不到
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.25,0:18:48.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那準備拿出來什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.70,0:18:49.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那邊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.82,0:18:56.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.02,0:19:11.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,騙人的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.09,0:19:16.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,討厭 喉嚨好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.63,0:19:18.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道妳想從這裡發射？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.93,0:19:22.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以才特意拿出這種東西的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.58,0:19:24.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,射偏了會怎樣？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.66,0:19:28.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係 你當我是誰
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.56,0:19:32.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的名字是『言靈使』
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.40,0:19:34.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果我說打中
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.65,0:19:36.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就會打中
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.51,0:19:44.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絕對給我打中
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.09,0:19:50.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.23,0:19:57.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那便是全力嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.15,0:20:01.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？風向改變了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.74,0:20:08.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這風是怎麼回事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.20,0:20:24.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,土地神！！！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.60,0:20:29.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟糕 不知不覺就出手了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.82,0:20:30.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,罰 金
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.19,0:20:31.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.23,0:20:34.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.62,0:20:36.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吶 看到了嗎？看到了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.68,0:20:38.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打中了對吧 打中了對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.66,0:20:42.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感覺軌跡最後有些改變啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.17,0:20:45.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,變化球？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.96,0:20:47.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呀 應該不是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.37,0:20:59.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直接給我落幕吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.49,0:21:10.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等不急啦 給我開花吧 『七鄉』
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.70,0:21:31.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,円神
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.71,0:21:38.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姬
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.34,0:23:30.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣的小姬我們不要啊3
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.54,0:23:36.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光吃蕎麥面的話 營養會跟不上的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.24,0:23:40.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呀 我有好好進行營養管理的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.67,0:23:43.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣的小姬我們不要啊4
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.72,0:23:45.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是姬 大家辛苦啦
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.01,0:23:47.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇 好噁心
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.20,0:23:48.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結束啦
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.21,0:23:54.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那櫻花盛開的城鎮
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.12,0:23:57.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我此決心一直未變
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.95,0:23:59.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喜歡花水木的妳的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.94,0:24:02.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將彷徨中的我指引向此方
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.45,0:24:05.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前方依然遍佈荊棘
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.08,0:24:07.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等待著妳的我邁出腳步
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.82,0:24:12.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在妳身前回首 淺唱小曲 開始前行
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.22,0:24:14.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們盼望著此時
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.96,0:24:17.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,櫻飛舞 我們共同前往此地
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.67,0:24:19.59,TITLE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(320,345)}櫻飛舞
